TITLE: Configuring Canvas Recording with Frame Rate Control and Image Format Settings
DESCRIPTION: Advanced configuration for Canvas recording with sampling rate and image format options. This limits Canvas recording to a maximum of 15 frames per second and specifies WebP format with 60% quality to optimize performance and storage.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rrweb-io/rrweb/blob/master/docs/recipes/canvas.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
