TITLE: Replaying Console Outputs in rrweb
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to configure rrweb to replay recorded console outputs during session replay. It demonstrates importing the replay console plugin and setting it up with specific log levels to be replayed.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rrweb-io/rrweb/blob/master/docs/recipes/console.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import rrweb from 'rrweb';
import { getReplayConsolePlugin } from '@rrweb/rrweb-plugin-console-replay';

const replayer = new rrweb.Replayer(events, {
  plugins: [
    getReplayConsolePlugin({
      level: ['info', 'log', 'warn', 'error'],
    }),
  ],
});
replayer.play();
```

