TITLE: Configuring rrweb Replayer with Canvas WebRTC Replay Plugin in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to set up the rrweb Replayer with the RRWebPluginCanvasWebRTCReplay plugin on the replay side. It initializes the plugin, configures callbacks for canvas discovery and signal sending, and sets up the replayer in live mode.
