TITLE: Enabling and Disabling UI Interaction in rrweb Replay
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to enable and disable user interaction with the replay UI using rrweb's API. By default, interaction is disabled using CSS pointer-events: none for stability, but it can be enabled for scenarios where user input during replay is desired.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rrweb-io/rrweb/blob/master/docs/recipes/interaction.zh_CN.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const replayer = new rrweb.Replayer(events);

// 允许用户在回放的 UI 中进行交互
replayer.enableInteract();

// 禁用用户在回放的 UI 中进行交互
replayer.disableInteract();
```

